        <div style="display:none;" id="pageTitle">SSC JE Previous Year Question Papers PDF (ME, CE and Electrical)</div>
        <div id="middleMain">
        <p>The SSC (Staff Selection Commission) conducts the Junior Engineer exam to recruit candidates for various engineering posts. The previous year’s paper provides valuable insights about the exam pattern and helps candidates in their exam preparation. By practising these papers, aspirants can develop confidence and boost their time management skills. The previous year’s paper will guide the candidate for the approximate distribution of questions as per the subjects and sub-topics.</p><h2 id="T17J54Y8LAE3HGMPT3UJI59D8OQNO85R">SSC JE Previous Year Question Papers</h2><p>SSC JE Previous Year Question Papers are an excellent resource for exam preparation. The selection process for <a href="https://www.careerpower.in/ssc-je.html" class="noStyle">SSC JE 2026</a> includes three stages: Paper 1: Computer-Based Test (CBT), Paper 2: Computer-Based Test (CBT), and Document Verification. The SSC Junior Engineer (JE) exam covers a variety of subjects, including general intelligence &amp; reasoning, general awareness, general engineering, estimation and costing, and building materials and environmental engineering.</p><h2 id="XV8J0AX6F56OWBQ8G3HTACHT9JUGP0EB">SSC JE Previous Year Question Papers PDF</h2><p>These SSC JE Previous Year Paper PDFs will help to understand the pattern &amp; type of questions asked by SSC. The exam pattern of SSC JE Recruitment involves two papers, i.e., Paper I &amp; Paper II. Only those candidates who will qualify for both Paper I &amp; Paper II will be called for document verification and a medical test. Paper I CBT consists of 200 questions for 200 marks, while Paper II consists of 100 questions for 300 marks. Candidates can download the papers in PDF format from the direct links provided below.</p><p><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/ssc-je-exam-date-2026"><strong>SSC JE Paper 2 Exam Date 2026 Out- Click to Check</strong></a></p><h3>SSC JE Civil Engineering Previous Year Papers</h3><h4>SSC JE Civil Paper 1 PDFs</h4><ul><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134228/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-Hindi-07-06-2024-S1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134229/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-Hindi-06-06-2024-S3.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134230/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-Hindi-06-06-2024-S1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134231/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-Hindi-05-06-2024-S1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134232/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-English-07-06-2024-S1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134233/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-English-06-06-2024-S3.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134235/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-English-06-06-2024-S1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134237/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-2024-in-English-05-06-2024-S1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19132717/SSC-JE-CIVIL-9-Oct-2023-Shift-1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2023 Question Paper&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21173358/Civil-Engineering-2022.pdf">Civil Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133708/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2022-15-11-2022-Shift-1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133705/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2022-15-11-2022-Shift-3.pdf">Civil Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133703/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2022-16-11-2022-Shift-1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133232/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2019-30-10-2020-Shift-3.pdf">Civil Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133235/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2019-30-10-2020-Shift-1.pdf">Civil Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133237/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2019-28-10-2020-Shift-3.pdf">Civil Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134536/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-29.October.2020-1st-Shift.pdf">Civil Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19133433/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2020-23-03-2021-Shift-3.pdf">Civil Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19132329/SSC-JE-CIVIL-2020-2.pdf">Civil Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19134729/SSC-JE-Civil-Question-Paper-23-March-2021-2nd-Shift-With-Answer.pdf">Civil Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21174027/Civil-Engineering-2019.pdf">Civil Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135132/SSC-JE-Civil-Paper-25-Sep-2019-1st-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Civil Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135133/SSC-JE-Civil-Paper-23-Sep-2019-3rd-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Civil Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135134/SSC-JE-Civil-Paper-23-Sep-2019-1st-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Civil Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21174206/Civil-Engineering-2018.pdf">Civil Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21174330/Civil-Engineering-2017.pdf">Civil Engineering 2017 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21174537/Civil-Engineering-2016.pdf">Civil Engineering-2016 Question Paper</a></li></ul><h4>SSC JE Civil Paper 2 PDFs</h4><ul><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21175027/Civil-Engineering-2023.pdf">Civil Engineering 2023 Paper 2 Question Paper</a></li></ul><h3>SSC JE Mechanical Previous Year Papers</h3><p>Paper 1:</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142321/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-2024-in-Hindi-07-06-2024-S2.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142323/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-2024-in-Hindi-05-06-2024-S2.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142325/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-2024-in-English-07-06-2024-S2.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142326/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-2024-in-English-05-06-2024-S2.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2024 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142327/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-22-March-2021-2nd-Shift-With-Answer.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142328/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-22-March-2021-1st-Shift-With-Answer.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142049/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-27.October.2020-3rd-Shift.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142051/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-28.October.2020-3rd-Shift-in-Hindi.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19142052/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Question-Paper-11.December.2020-1st-Shift.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19141628/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Paper-27-Sep-2019-3rd-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19141629/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Paper-27-Sep-2019-1st-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19141632/SSC-JE-Mechanical-Paper-25-Sep-2019-3rd-Shift-English.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21175457/Mechanical-Engineering-2018-1.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2018 Question Paper&nbsp;</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21175753/Mechanical-Engineering-2017.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2017 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21175936/Mechanical-Engineering-2015.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2015 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21180054/Mechanical-Engineering-2016.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2016 Question Paper</a></li></ul><p><strong>Paper 2:</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21180347/Mechanical-Engineering.pdf">Mechanical Engineering Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21180441/Mechanical-Engineering-2023.pdf">Mechanical Engineering 2023 Question Paper</a></li></ul><h3>SSC JE Electrical Engineering Previous Year Papers</h3><p><strong>Paper 1:</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21181017/Electrical-Engineering-2022.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140944/SSC-JE-Electrical-Question-Paper-16-November-2022-PDF.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140943/SSC-JE-Electrical-Question-Paper-15-November-2022-PDF.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2022 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21181112/Electrical-Engineering-2020-21.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140601/SSC-JE-Electrical-Question-Paper-24-March-2021-2nd-Shift-With-Answer.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2021 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140604/SSC-JE-Electrical-Question-Paper-10.December.2020-3rd-Shift.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140603/SSC-JE-Electrical-Question-Paper-28.October.2020-1st-Shift.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2020 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140208/SSC-JE-Electrical-Paper-1-with-Key-PDF-26-9-2019-1st-shift_unlocked.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140208/SSC-JE-Electrical-Paper-1-with-Key-PDF-26-9-2019-3rd-shift_unlocked.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140207/SSC-JE-Electrical-Paper-26-Sep-2019-1st-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19140205/SSC-JE-Electrical-Paper-26-Sep-2019-3rd-Shift-Hindi.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2019 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21181216/Electrical-Engineering-2018.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135830/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-27-1-2018-EV.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135831/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-25-1-2018-MR.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135833/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-25-1-2018-EV.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135835/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-24-1-2018-MR.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135836/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-24-1-2018-EV.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135838/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-23-1-2018-MR.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135839/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-23-1-2018-EV.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/19135841/SSC-JE-EE-PAPER-22-1-2018-MR.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2018 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21181301/Electrical-Engineering-2016.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2016 Question Paper</a></li></ul><p><strong>Paper 2:</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21181553/Electrical-Engineering.pdf">Electrical Engineering Paper 2 Question Paper</a></li><li><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/21181636/Electrical-Engineering-2023.pdf">Electrical Engineering 2023 Question Paper</a></li></ul><h3>Benefits of Solving the SSC JE Previous Year Paper</h3><ul><li>Practice with previous year papers: essential for exam success</li><li>Understand exam pattern and difficulty: Gain insights from previous papers</li><li>Increase chances of selection: Boost your confidence and knowledge</li><li>Identifying strengths and weaknesses: recognise areas of excellence and improvement</li><li>Targeted preparation: Focus on weaker topics to enhance overall performance</li><li>Time Management: Practice solving papers within the allotted time</li><li>Confidence Boost: Enhance your confidence and reduce exam anxiety</li></ul><figure class="table"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan="2"><strong>Related Links</strong></td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/ssc-je-syllabus.html"><strong>SSC JE Syllabus 2025</strong></a></td><td><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/ssc-je-exam-pattern.html"><strong>&nbsp;SSC JE Exam Pattern 2025</strong></a></td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/ssc-je-cut-off.html"><strong>SSC JE Cut Off [Previous Year]</strong></a></td><td><a href="https://www.careerpower.in/blog/ssc-calendar-2025"><strong>SSC Calendar 2025</strong></a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
