        <section id='faqs' class='faqs'>
      <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample"><div id="faq" class="faq-heading">SSC JE  Previous Year Question Papers-FAQs</div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <p class=" accordion-header" id="heading0">
            <button class="accordion-button  collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse0"
              aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse0">
              Q1.Are SSC JE Previous Year Question Papers helpful?
            </button>
          </p>
          <div id="collapse0" class="accordion-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="heading0"
            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Ans. Yes, by practising SSC JE Previous Year Question Papers, the candidates understand the level of questions asked in the exam & difficulty level in a much better way.
            </div>
          </div>
        
      </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <p class=" accordion-header" id="heading1">
            <button class="accordion-button  collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1"
              aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
              Q2. What are the sections or subjects in the SSC JE H exam?
            </button>
          </p>
          <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="heading1"
            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Ans The subjects in SSC JE are  general intelligence & reasoning, general awareness, general engineering, estimation and costing, and building materials and environmental engineering.
            </div>
          </div>
        
      </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <p class=" accordion-header" id="heading2">
